init_text: Humans once wielded formidable magical power. But with over 7 billion of us on the planet now, Mana has spread far too thinly to have any effect. When hostile aliens reduce humanity to a mere fraction, the survivors discover an old power has begun to reawaken once again.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: As the war rages on, the humans begin to realize that the aliens have been manipulating them for thousands of years.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The aliens have been using humanity as a tool to help them achieve their own goals.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The humans must fight back against the aliens and their own ancient magic to prevent the aliens from achieving their goal.
